# Git Attributes for Smart Secrets Scanner Project

# Mark documentation and research files as linguist-documentation
# This helps GitHub understand these files contain EXAMPLE secrets for educational purposes
# and should not trigger secret scanning alerts

# Research and documentation files with example secrets
research/**/*.md linguist-documentation
tasks/**/*.md linguist-documentation
data/README.md linguist-documentation
data/HOW_TO_USE_DATASET.md linguist-documentation
EXECUTION_GUIDE.md linguist-documentation
README.md linguist-documentation

# All markdown files are documentation
*.md linguist-documentation

# Ensure consistent line endings
* text=auto
*.py text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf
*.md text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.jsonl text eol=lf

# Binary files
*.bin binary
*.safetensors binary
*.gguf binary
*.pt binary
*.pth binary
*.pkl binary
